OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774947927
OL,3,CVoluntary sector cuts put young people
OL,4,Cat risk, Children's Commissioner warns
OL,6,FBy Maria Hassan
OL,8,FThe Children's Commissioner has warned
OL,9,Fcommunity funding cuts will put young
OL,10,Fpeople in Northern Ireland at risk.
OL,12,FYouth organisations are facing a
OL,13,Ffinancial cliff-edge when the UK
OL,14,FShared Prosperity Fund is replaced by
OL,15,Fthe Local Growth Fund on April 1,
OL,16,Freducing funding for voluntary groups
OL,17,Fby 64%.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774947927
OL,3,CVoluntary sector cuts put young people
OL,4,Cat risk, Children's Commissioner warns
OL,6,FThe Executive and the community sector
OL,7,Fhave called for the decision to be
OL,8,Freversed to reflect local need. The
OL,9,Fgovernment maintains the Executive has
OL,10,Fthe funds to provide additional
OL,11,Fsupport, if it wishes
OL,13,FIn 2023, EU funding to charities and
OL,14,Fcommunity groups in Northern Ireland
OL,15,Ffrom the European Social Fund was
OL,16,Fended because of Brexit.
OL,18,FIt was replaced by the UK Shared
OL,19,FProsperity Fund, which will in turn be
OL,20,Freplaced by the Local Growth Fund from
OL,21,FApril 1.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774947927
OL,3,CVoluntary sector cuts put young people
OL,4,Cat risk, Children's Commissioner warns
OL,6,FThat new fund has a 70/30 capital-to-
OL,7,Frevenue split, resulting in funding
OL,8,Fcuts to the voluntary sector.
OL,10,FThe Bytes project in Glengormley is
OL,11,Fone of 7 charities in the YouthStart
OL,12,Fconsortium who are currently
OL,13,Fsupporting more than 1,300 young
OL,14,Fpeople.
OL,16,FParticipants told UTV about the
OL,17,Fpositive influence the services have
OL,18,Fhad on them.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774947927
OL,3,CVoluntary sector cuts put young people
OL,4,Cat risk, Children's Commissioner warns
OL,6,F"I feel like Bytes project is possibly
OL,7,Fthe most important thing to me in my
OL,8,Flife right now.
OL,10,F"It has helped me through so much
OL,11,Fmental baggage and allowed me to speak
OL,12,Fto people that I genuinely trust and
OL,13,Fenjoy spending time with," Aidan said.
OL,15,FFor these organisations, the reduction
OL,16,Fin the Local Growth Fund pot means the
OL,17,Fwithdrawal of support for more than
OL,18,F800 youth participants.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774947927
OL,3,CVoluntary sector cuts put young people
OL,4,Cat risk, Children's Commissioner warns
OL,6,FProvision in the Ards and North Down
OL,7,Fand Mid-Ulster council areas is
OL,8,Fstopping completely with more than 30
OL,9,Fyouth workers facing redundancy.
OL,11,FThe consortium has warned that the
OL,12,Fdecision puts young people - many of
OL,13,Fwhom are already experiencing a range
OL,14,Fof life challenges - at a disadvantage
OL,15,Fwith less or no contact with their
OL,16,Fyouth worker, meaning reduced well-
OL,17,Fbeing support, pastoral care and
OL,18,Femployability advice.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774947927
OL,3,CVoluntary sector cuts put young people
OL,4,Cat risk, Children's Commissioner warns
OL,6,FBytes CEO Stephen Dallas said: "These
OL,7,Fare spaces where you will find a
OL,8,Ftrusted adult, something to eat and
OL,9,Finformal learning outside of the
OL,10,Fschool context.
OL,12,F"Why on earth would you make that less
OL,13,Fof an investment?
OL,15,F"This is about young people and their
OL,16,Fvalue in our society."
OL,18,FChildren's Commissioner Chris Quinn is
OL,19,Fconcerned that young people will fall
OL,20,Fthrough the cracks.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774947927
OL,3,CVoluntary sector cuts put young people
OL,4,Cat risk, Children's Commissioner warns
OL,6,F"Voluntary sector providers, they're
OL,7,Fthe people who step in when when
OL,8,Fstatutory services fail.
OL,10,F"What we're talking about here are
OL,11,Fvulnerable young people who are
OL,12,Fengaging at community level with
OL,13,Fpeople in in safe spaces, and it's
OL,14,Fmore this is more than about a safe
OL,15,Fspace to go or, you know, engaging in
OL,16,Frecreational activity.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774947927
OL,3,CVoluntary sector cuts put young people
OL,4,Cat risk, Children's Commissioner warns
OL,6,F"This is about non-formal education,
OL,7,Fthis is about personal development,
OL,8,Fthis is about getting closer to
OL,9,Feconomic activity but for some young
OL,10,Fpeople, this is about staying alive,"
OL,11,Fhe said.
OL,13,FQuestions have also been raised about
OL,14,Fthe statutory footing youth work is on.
OL,16,F"We need to work harder to protect
OL,17,Fyouth services locally ... How we make
OL,18,Fthe law stronger to protect children
OL,19,Fand young people because our policies
OL,20,Fand laws I would say are out of date,"
OL,21,Fthe Commissioner added.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
