PN,44809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774947927
OL,3,CVoluntary sector cuts put young people
OL,4,Cat risk, Children's Commissioner warns
OL,6,FResearch, led by Ulster University, is
OL,7,Fcurrently evaluating the impact of
OL,8,Fthese projects on young people's lives
OL,9,Fand wider society.
OL,11,FDr Ciara Fitzpatrick said: "Analysis
OL,12,Fof the labour force survey showed a
OL,13,F50% increase in the number of young
OL,14,Fpeople who are currently not in
OL,15,Femployment over a 12 month period.
OL,16,FThat is really significant.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
