CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774947927
OL,3,CVoluntary sector cuts put young people
OL,4,Cat risk, Children's Commissioner warns
OL,6,F"We are essentially going to see that
OL,7,Ffigure increasing again, because young
OL,8,Fpeople don't have the access to that
OL,9,Fone on one, holistic personal approach
OL,10,Fthat really tackles huge issues that
OL,11,Fparticularly our disadvantaged young
OL,12,Fpeople are facing at the minute,
OL,13,Fwhether that be mental health issues,
OL,14,Faddiction issues, young mums who are
OL,15,Fstruggling to cope.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/18
