CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774947927
OL,3,CVoluntary sector cuts put young people
OL,4,Cat risk, Children's Commissioner warns
OL,6,F"Or young people who are in a real
OL,7,Ftransition in life. They've maybe left
OL,8,Fschool, they don't know where to go
OL,9,Fnext, they don't know where to seek
OL,10,Finformation and they maybe don't have
OL,11,Ffamily support .... they really need
OL,12,Fthis sort of intensive approach that
OL,13,Fyouth work provides."
OL,15,FThe government has been facing
OL,16,Fpressure from the Executive and the
OL,17,Fsector to reverse the decision to
OL,18,Freflect local need.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/18
