PN,44816
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774947927
OL,3,CVoluntary sector cuts put young people
OL,4,Cat risk, Children's Commissioner warns
OL,6,FA government spokesperson said: "The
OL,7,FLocal Growth Fund will support the
OL,8,Fdelivery of long-term infrastructure
OL,9,Fto boost economic growth across the UK.
OL,11,F"Northern Ireland will receive #45.5m
OL,12,Fin each of the next three years, on
OL,13,Ftop of its record #19.3bn annual
OL,14,Ffunding settlement.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/18
