OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44817
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774947927
OL,3,CVoluntary sector cuts put young people
OL,4,Cat risk, Children's Commissioner warns
OL,6,F"This settlement - as well as the #370
OL,7,Fmillion announced at the Budget and
OL,8,Fthe further #379m in resource funding
OL,9,Fannounced by the Chancellor on Tuesday
OL,10,F3 March, gives the NI Executive with
OL,11,Fthe means to provide additional
OL,12,Ffunding to support the voluntary and
OL,13,Fcommunity sector through resource
OL,14,Ffunding, if it wishes to.
OL,16,F"We are working in partnership with
OL,17,Fthe Northern Ireland Executive to
OL,18,Fdesign and deliver the Local Growth
OL,19,FFund in Northern Ireland."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G17/18
